    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on how property rights play into this? Like, if a platform is private, does the government even have a right to tell them how to moderate, or is that just another form of censorship of the users' rights? I want to make the argument that the current regulatory approach is fundamentally flawed from a libertarian perspective.",
